,Recommended,427820,28719626,"Posted: 27 December, 2016",all,NarutoDeWitt,"I've got to say this is no Hitman you know and love. It's a whole new sexy twist.This Hitman-themed puzzle game is carefully crafted in detail. Each and every level is carefully designed to look just like a normal game board, but don't let the board-game-like appearance fool you. The game mechanics is very easy to understand, which leads to intriguing puzzles and challenges it offers. Sure, you won't be able to be so creative at eliminating your enemies like many Hitman games, but it still gives you some room to think of other possible solutions, leading to completing challenges. Also, like many good puzzle games, you will be delighted to be able to solve it and would wish to see your own solution again. You might even think ""Wow I never thought I could do that. That's amazing!"". The soundtrack within the game is also very cool. Along with the lighting and the board design, this is the sexiest Hitman I've ever seen.On the downside, the number of levels in this game is too few, and I can finish the whole game in a couple of days. I wish it could have more levels than this, or just give us regular updates for new levels just like the 2016 Hitman. Also, yes, this is just the same Hitman GO on iOS and Android devices, so if you have played on one of those devices, I'm afraid you'll be playing the same levels all over again with more beautiful graphics."
